data.description: Basement rancher in a convenient location to Morristown. This home is 4 bedrooms, but 1 bedroom is being used as an upstairs laundry room. Can easily be reverted back into the 4th bedroom. Home has lots of extra space, and is perfect for a large family. Step out your back door and admire the beautiful views of Cherokee Lake, and has a large, new deck on the back of the home. Don't miss out! Seller is relocating and priced to sell!
